# INSTRUCTIONS FOR DEPLOYMENT

Make Sure you create database to existing postgres

```bash
psql -U zalongwa -h localhost -p 5432 postgres

CREATE DATABASE cuf_db;

\l
```

Update `SECRET_KEY` and `DEBUG` mode  in .env

```bash
cp .env.example .env

cp docker-compose.prod.yml docker-compose.yml

docker compose up -d --build
```

extra for temporary data backup

```bash
mkdir fixtures
docker compose exec cuf_website python manage.py dumpdata admin_app --indent 4 > fixtures/admin_app.json
docker compose exec cuf_website python manage.py dumpdata main_app --indent 4 > fixtures/main_app.json

docker compose exec cuf_website python manage.py loaddata fixtures/user.json
```